AD_REFERENCE.NAME: Print Providers
AD_REFERENCE.DESCRIPTION: Select the Print Provider whose printers you want to refresh.
AD_REFERENCE.HELP: Choose the provider configuration (created in Print Providers) that the refresh process will use. The selection determines: -Credentials & endpoints: the process reads the providerâ€™s API Key, Printers GET URL and other settings. -Implementation: it loads the Java class mapped in Providers Implementation for this provider. -Scope: only printers that belong to the selected provider (and your organisation) will be added/updated.
